author: mwebb
msg: This is an initial prototype of the SPDY protocol (http://dev.chromium.org/spdy/spdy-protocol).  With this initial check-in, I have accomplished the following:
1. I have each SPDY Frame type represented in a class
2. Written protocol encoder/decoder for sending and receiving of data using the SPDY protocol
There is much left to do.  Please see the TODO file in the top level of this package.
